{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"743","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"碳排放統計 工業、服務業減最多","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>工商時報 馮建棨<span lang='EN-US'> 2020.07.22</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%A2%B3%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 410px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>今年排碳大戶仍是工業，占整體<span lang='EN-US'>48.9</span>％，其次是能源與運輸，分別占<span lang='EN-US'>14.5</span>％及<span lang='EN-US'>14.0</span>％。圖<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>本報資料照片</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟部能源局<span lang='EN-US'>21</span>日公布最新能源類別碳排放統計指出，因能源消費去年比前年減少<span lang='EN-US'>0.6</span>％，主要是工業及服務類減少最多，分別年減<span lang='EN-US'>4.42</span>％及<span lang='EN-US'>4.56</span>％，僅有運輸部門年增<span lang='EN-US'>0.59</span>％。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>能源局表示，工業部門排放減少<span lang='EN-US'>585</span>萬公噸，年減<span lang='EN-US'>4.4</span>％，主要是各產業生產指數多呈下降趨勢，以致整體能源消費減少<span lang='EN-US'>2.1</span>％，其中非電力能源消費減少<span lang='EN-US'>3.4</span>％，電力消費則減少<span lang='EN-US'>1.0</span>％，加上電力排碳係數下降所致，工業部門排放呈減少趨勢。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>官員說，政府持續推動增氣減煤，讓生煤使用量持續下降，其中電力排碳係數下降<span lang='EN-US'>4.5</span>％。另外去年年燃料燃燒二氧化碳排放量為<span lang='EN-US'>2.58</span>億公噸，比前年的<span lang='EN-US'>2.67</span>億公噸減少<span lang='EN-US'>3.2</span>％，唯有運輸部門較去年增加<span lang='EN-US'>0.6</span>％，整體排放量都呈現減少趨勢。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>值得注意的是，今年排碳大戶仍是工業，占整體<span lang='EN-US'>48.9</span>％，其次是能源與運輸，分別占<span lang='EN-US'>14.5</span>％及<span lang='EN-US'>14.0</span>％，另外住宅部門碳排占整體<span lang='EN-US'>11.0</span>％，服務業部門<span lang='EN-US'>10.4</span>％，農業部門排放量占比最小，僅占<span lang='EN-US'>1.2</span>％</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>能源局強調，去年燃料燃燒二氧化碳排放量已較前年減少，顯示我國溫室氣體排放已朝<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年淨排放較<span lang='EN-US'>2005</span>年減<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>％的第一期階段管制目標邁進，未來透過持續推動部門減碳與能源轉型，達成減碳目標。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ctee.com.tw/news/policy/304835.html</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-07-22","clk_count":"283"}},"__N_SSG":true}